		<RichText x="57" y="853" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="32" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="252" height="36" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="32" color="#ffffff">Wt/Ed: 300/400</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#99ffe5" distance="10" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="65" y="452" fontFamily="SDK_SC_Web" fontSize="24" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="337" height="30" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="SDK_SC_Web" fontSize="24" fontStyle="italic" color="#ffffff">“The Homesick Lone Wolf”</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#99ffe5" distance="10" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">孤狼对玩家进行至多抓，咬，咬3段攻击，依次造成<span color="#7fffd7">50%,40%,70%</span><span>伤害，可单独施放。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="413" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">孤狼朝玩家凶猛袭来，并用力切割两次，每次造成<span color="#7fffd7">70%</span><span>伤害，可连续施放2次。无蕴光效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="437" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">孤狼迅速高跳至玩家处，并踉跄一下，造成<span color="#7fffd7">100%</span><span>伤害。召唤狼魂之前返回场地中央时立即施放。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="399" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">孤狼用利爪用力劈开一刀风刃，造成<span color="#7fffd7">90%</span><span>伤害。无蕴光效果。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="799" width="424" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">一段时间后，或低于<span color="#ffbfbf">70%</span><span>生命值时，孤狼移至场地中央，召唤</span><span textDecoration="underline">先祖狼魂</span><span>，狼魂会效仿孤狼的攻击造成</span><span color="#99ffff">冰元素</span><span>伤害，期间孤狼的抗性大幅提升。<br/>狼魂不能够被直接命中，仅能通过在孤狼身上扩散</span><span color="#ffacff">雷</span><span color="#ff9999">火</span><span>元素命中。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="399" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">孤狼朝前方猛地喷吐狂风，造成造成<span color="#7fffd7">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1087" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">孤狼与狼魂一起朝地面喷吐暴风与狂霜，在地面上随机生成风刺与冰刺，造成基于各自<span color="#ffffbf">30%</span><span>攻击力的伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
