			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">先祖狼魂：<span color="#99ffff">12冻</span><span>盾，仅能被</span><span color="#ffacff">雷扩散</span><span>与</span><span color="#ff9999">火扩散</span><span>命中，可以被选中瞄准，破盾后消散使孤狼瘫痪13s。狼魂的攻击力为孤狼的</span><span color="#ffbfbf">5/8</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
